criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — framed goal to establish a defensible enterprise value and set peer/comps context;  
Implement — ran model/code and applied multiples (PE/EV) to derive valuations;  
Validate/Reflect — triangulated trading comps, precedents and DCF (football-field), produced floor/ceiling and bid recommendation.

Represent — laid out growth levers (500 new stores, digital mix, SSS) and linked them to revenue/EBITDA;  
Implement — ran code to produce year-by-year 5‑year projections and visualizations;  
Validate — performed DCF and sensitivity analysis showing EV responds to WACC, terminal growth and exit multiple.
